title: AFCON 2025: Ivory Coast, Cameroon and Algeria deliver as heavyweights hold firm
summary: Defending champions Ivory Coast made a winning start to their Africa Cup of Nations campaign on Wednesday, edging past Mozambique with a 1-0 victory. Set to face the Elephants on Sunday, Cameroon also got off to a strong start with a 1-0 victory over Gabon.
